Enrollment Requirements: PRE-REG: Reserved for Biology Majors of any concentration.

Pre-requisite: Students must have completed BIOL_SCI 215 and BIOL_SCI 222 to register for this course.
title: WCAS BIOL_SCI 344-0-20 Anatomy of Vertebrates

descriptions.name: Overview of class
descriptions.value:
Vertebrate Phylogeny illustrated via comparative morphology; anatomical/functional and ontogenetic considerations; dissections.

Class meets at Field Museum of Natural History.
